responseText: So, you're new huh? Don't bother arguing, I can almost smell it on you. It's alright, more and more settlers coming through every day. Glory to the Goddess, right? I'm with the Striders Vigilant, you may not know us, but we're looking out for you folks. In fact, we're looking for help with a bit of a collection we've taken up. Would you like to help out?
name: SQ_Lionhold_Clotharmor_Timony_1_Response
